function execute(params, inputs, outputs) {
    print("!!!! " + inputs.x1) 
    print("!!!! Platform: " + params._sys.platform)
    outputs.x1 = inputs.x1
    outputs.x2 = [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6]
    outputs.x2.blockLength = 3
    outputs.a = inputs.x1[10] + inputs.x1[20]
    outputs.m1 = inputs.m1
    return "Hello from JS!"
}
